Pre-Game Insights: Finidi George made three changes to the starting lineup for the match against Benin, including dropping Kelechi Iheanacho and introducing Samuel Chukwueze, Raphael Onyedika, and Benjamin Tanimu. The team aims to secure their first win in the World Cup qualifiers after drawing 1-1 against South Africa.
The match against Benin will start at 5pm Nigerian time.
